WEBVTT

00:01.160 --> 00:02.639
'Previously on Camelot...'

00:02.760 --> 00:04.352
(Merlin) 'The legend's clear.

00:04.480 --> 00:06.277
'Whoever pulls the sword from that rock

00:06.400 --> 00:08.516
'shall be the king to unite all of Britain.'

00:08.640 --> 00:12.997
I present to you
your undoubted King.

00:14.120 --> 00:15.997
And every king needs his champions.

00:16.120 --> 00:19.999
So, I call upon Leontes,
to whom I owe my life.

00:20.120 --> 00:23.715
(Arthur) I had a dream,
maybe a vision, of you.

00:23.840 --> 00:26.274
Guinevere, this is the amazing Leontes.

00:26.400 --> 00:28.960
Actually, we've known each other
a very long time.

00:29.080 --> 00:30.752
This is my betrothed.

00:30.880 --> 00:32.359
I am.

00:32.479 --> 00:34.596
(Morgan) 'I'm Uther's daughter
and sole heir.

00:34.720 --> 00:36.551
'This castle and realm should be mine.'

00:36.680 --> 00:40.355
We don't need to be opposed.
We can work together.

00:40.480 --> 00:41.913
For you, this is nothing.

00:42.040 --> 00:44.474
For me, everything.

